HEADWORD: Rhinestone
<hw>Rhine"stone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. G.
<ets>rheinkiesel</ets> Rhine quartz.]</ety> <def>A colorless stone of
high luster, made of paste. It is much used as an inexpensive
ornament.</def>⟦br⟧
